{"success": true, "message": "Fetched question.", "data": {"showTimer": true, "showAttemptInsight": true, "playSounds": true, "dontShowCorrectAnswerImmediately": false, "_id": "64c0e7ad6f5bfc7ab78ae6eb", "classes": [], "exams": ["615d7713c52ffa3c944600e3"], "subjects": ["615d708dbd4a37c4058ee5a8"], "chapters": ["615d6fed2b295b085ab6eb9b"], "topics": [], "concepts": [], "previousYearPapers": [{"_id": "61a8bf0fc821b6514e527d77", "title": "BITSAT 2013", "isVisible": true}], "position": 0, "type": "singleCorrect", "level": 2, "approximateTimeRequired": 90, "question": {"text": "Two identical capacitors, have the same capacitance $\\mathrm{C}$. One of them is charged to potential $\\mathrm{V}_{1}$ and the other to $\\mathrm{V}_{2}$. The negative ends of the capacitors are connected together. When the positive ends are also connected, the decrease in energy of the combined system is -", "image": null}, "options": [{"id": "MVPpr", "text": "$\\frac{1}{4} \\mathrm{C}\\left(\\mathrm{V}_{1}^{2}-\\mathrm{V}_{2}^{2}\\right)$", "isCorrect": false, "image": null}, {"id": "nwRYW", "text": "$\\frac{1}{4} C\\left(V_{1}^{2}+V_{2}^{2}\\right)$", "isCorrect": false, "image": null}, {"id": "ctNqY", "text": "$\\frac{1}{4} \\mathrm{C}\\left(\\mathrm{V}_{1}-\\mathrm{V}_{2}\\right)^{2}$", "isCorrect": true, "image": null}, {"id": "h1PLt", "text": "$\\frac{1}{4} C\\left(V_{1}+V_{2}\\right)^{2}$", "isCorrect": false, "image": null}], "correctValue": null, "solution": {"text": "Initial energy of combined system\r\n\r\n$$\r\n\r\n\\mathrm{U}_{1}=\\frac{1}{2} \\mathrm{CV}_{1}^{2}+\\frac{1}{2} \\mathrm{CV}_{2}^{2}\r\n\r\n$$\r\n\r\nFinal common potential, $\\mathrm{V}=\\frac{\\mathrm{V}_{1}+\\mathrm{V}_{2}}{2},$\r\n\r\nFinal energy of system,\r\n\r\n$$\r\n\r\n\\mathrm{U}_{2}=2 \\times \\frac{1}{2} \\mathrm{C}\\left(\\frac{\\mathrm{V}_{1}+\\mathrm{V}_{2}}{2}\\right)^{2}\r\n\r\n$$\r\n\r\nHence loss of energy $=\\mathrm{U}_{1}-\\mathrm{U}_{2}$\r\n\r\n$$\r\n\r\n=\\frac{1}{4} \\mathrm{C}\\left(\\mathrm{V}_{1}-\\mathrm{V}_{2}\\right)^{2}\r\n\r\n$$", "image": null}, "videoSolution": null, "numericalUpperLimit": null, "numericalLowerLimit": null, "questionLabels": [], "__v": 0, "masterId": "MOGBSPYQ90414065", "bucket": "", "category": null, "microConcepts": [], "imageBaseUrl": null, "helperText": null, "isRemoved": false, "cpyqbSubjects": ["61bb58181213731910ea0b70", "61c055eae8ce0dc8a5c62d33", "616057750283de43c87e3e1b", "61964fe0a5a5260118868021", "61964f81a5a526011886801d", "629f39e4ac11b26562e0625b", "616057920283de43c87e3e1e", "615f0c729476412f48314dab", "61a8a2c2e8ce0dc8a5c62d2d", "629105adee9e3ae00d63352b", "629f385f263330a77be9fa7d", "616056cd0283de43c87e3e15", "616057190283de43c87e3e18", "62962075e7f8e9ac4daeafd7", "64d50bd73df7f4a7f3017f6f", "66b79b34d4b564dfab4f94cc", "678ea9a09cc79e5f592bdc11", "67fa5fef4468eb1307ceb0ad", "6807d2ad647479b8e8696479"], "cpyqbChapters": ["6160240bda5af4913929a0b8", "620ab21cec588a56880df090", "6160240a212e155ed4960db3", "61964c89e2db387e83a2dc00", "61964c886e5c35cfbefd2bfb", "61c0899734a1d89d41763668", "61bb82180b1fbc28a038c245", "61e7bd750f84ffa5822273d0", "629f390a342194584e0c4a47", "629109eaba274a157c178056", "629621215633194fad7124dc", "629f3a8f3249600beac1cf57", "64eb06c23118f713ecfef08a", "66d5853aa75f05ee8564f570", "67921d6b1d5b5072da5e9ae6", "67fdff57378e1624ea7b6a6e", "680920313a10446a207fdf28"], "cpyqbExams": ["61a8a124e8ce0dc8a5c62d2c"]}, "fetch_status": true}